+R18-BLOCKING-07：无 git status before/after	已提供，但 after status 与“18 remaining”不一致	PARTIALLY_CLOSED
+Remaining Blockers
+R18-BLOCKING-03：pre-commit hook evidence 仍不是原始证据
+
+sadp-audit-output-commit-1..6.txt 都包含同一句关键说明：
