+YAML
+R18-BLOCKING-03:
+  status: OPEN
+  reason: per-commit sadp-audit evidence is reconstructed, not raw machine output
+R18-BLOCKING-04：ai_guard.py evidence 实际没有覆盖 3,634 文件
